<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title> Bee Learning Activation Email</title>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <style type="text/css">
            /* BASE */
            body{
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                min-width: 100;
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                background-color: #000000;
                color: #ffffff;
            }
            a{
                color: #000;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            h1{
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 1.25;
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            p {
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }
            table td{
                vertical-align: top;
            }

            /* LAYOUT */
            .email-wrapper{
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .email-header{
                background-color: #F8AB11;
                padding: 24px;
                color: #ffff;

            }
            .email-body {
                padding: 24px;
                background-color: #130E06;
            }
            .email-footer{
                background-color: #5B5850;
                padding: 24px;
            }

            /* BUTTON */
            .button{
                display: inline-block;
                background-color: #0070f3;
                color: #ffff;
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: 700;
                text-align: center;
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="email-header">
                <h1>Welcome to Bee Learning</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
                <p>Thank you for registering with Bee Learning. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
                <h2> <%= activationCode %></h2>
                <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
                <p>If you did not register for Bee Learning account, please ignore this email</p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-footer">
                <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:mwangeamusa@gmail.com">mwangeamusa@gmail.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>